    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Protective helmets for the benefit of fighter pilots. From the advent of jet aircraft these have been equipped with visors and provisions for communications, breathing, or other equipment.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
